pr_title: [OODT-1035][OODT-1037] Improve UI/UX of Workflow Manager Components in React.js OPSUI
pr_body:
Included changes:

1. Display past/present workflows in a paginated table view
2. Write new api endpoint to get paginated workflow pages
3. add missing api to the swagger api definitions
4. Implement triggering workflows by sending events from the OPSUI
5. Fix the issues mentioned in [OODT-1037](https://issues.apache.org/jira/projects/OODT/issues/OODT-1037?filter=allopenissues)

pr_title: Improve UI/UX of File Manager Components in React.js OPSUI
pr_body:
Included changes:  
1. Replace alerts with snack bar using notistack npm package
2. Improve snack bar styles
3. Remove unused code and comments
4. Improve Product Browser UI by displaying products in a paginated table
5. Remove redundant file manager endpoints 
6. Display product data inside the product browser itself by means of a drawer

pr_title: Improve product browser and product ingest UI
pr_body:
Included changes:

1. Add progress bars to display the progress of file ingestion processes.
2. Fix product browser pagination
3. Create a new endpoint to get product types
4. Improve search bar UI
5. Move file manager REST api calls to a separate dedicated module.
